    "The authors found ChatGPT scored the lowest on Step 1 material amongst all three question types when indeterminate answers were included [5].",
    "As Step 1 is largely basic science and pathology based, these results contrast with observations seen in our study.",
    "The OITE covers 11 domains of Orthopedics and incorporates radiographs and current treatment standards for common pathophysiology into its question sets [9].",
    "ChatGPT answered 19/22 (86.4%) of Orthopedic Basic Science questions correct with 1 out of 3 incorrect responses still demonstrating consistent logic with the testmakers (IC group).",
